is equally valued, pure swaps of GREEN for another chip are zero-sum for value and only useful instrumentally (e.g., to bundle or re-balance). Most efficiency gains will come from moving RED away from squid toward camel and badger, and moving BLUE away from camel toward badger and squid. The following forecast instantiates one plausible full play-through where players gradually discover these complementarities, with some declined proposals early and more accepted trades once they infer each other's preferences.",
